            "title": "盤中速報 - Palo Alto Networks Inc(PANW-US)大漲5.09%，報154.5美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Palo Alto Networks Inc(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PANW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PANW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PANW-US</a>)截至台北時間30日21:37股價上漲7.48美元，報154.50美元，漲幅5.09%，成交量899,357（股），盤中最高價154.52美元、最低價151.47美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.62%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.41%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.44%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.14%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Palo Alto Networks Inc(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PANW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PANW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PANW-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-9.78%</li> <li>近 1 月：-1.28%</li> <li>近 3 月：-21.32%</li> <li>近 6 月：-27.92%</li> <li>今年以來：-20.18%</li></ul></section></main>",
